title: South Korea 52 Week Bill Yield
description: South Korea 1 Year Bond Yield was 3.94 percent on Tuesday November 8, according to over-the-counter interbank yield quotes for this government bond maturity. Historically, the South Korea 52 Week Bill Yield reached an all time high of 5.81 in January of 2008. This page includes a chart with historical data for South Korea 52W.
